Step 1.
    Download ui.router Module by using bower.

Step 2.
    Add the ui.router Module Dependency. 

Step 3.
    Create the Target Templates  

Step 4.         
    Create the Controllers

Step 5.
    Do the Mapping

Ex.
    [login.html
      loginController]

    [home.html
     homeController] 

 - Mapping Should done before launching the Angular Application.
   (constructor) 
   //app.config(config) 

 - To do the Mapping ANgular Framework provides Predefined Objects.
    - $stateProvider
    - $urlRouterProvider

 - Mapping Should Done in the form of a "key&value" pairs.

    login   ----->  login.html & loginController
    home    ----->  home.html & homeController   


Step 6.
    Create the Source Template.

 Ex. 

 index.html       